    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For now you could always do it very hacky way by showing/hiding facet blocks by looking at the number of facet values you get in a render() call of a specific widget (or just by subscribing to the helper.on('results') event.\n\nAs for providing an option to do it directly in instantsearch.js => everything is doable but needs an API entry that is making sense and easy to name. Go for it :)\n",
