    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is either solved by creating a guide on \"How to conditionnaly display widgets\" or we could also allow users to provide a custom function to the autoHideContainer option where they can return true/false given the dataset.\n\n``` js\nautoHideContainer: function(facetValues) {\n  if (facetValues.length === 1) return false;\n  return true;\n}\n```\n",
